item.title: trader joes holiday haul & review (using python just for fun)
item.description: Happy holidays to everyone! Last week, a couple of my friends and I bought some of the holiday snacks/products at trader joes to taste test and review. We gave each item a rating from 1-10 and the ratings are in the order [Mark, Allison, Devika]. Here are our takes: Mini Gingerbread People [5,6.5,8.5] Peppermint Chocolate Chunk Cookie Mix [7,6,6] Dark Chocolate Covered Peppermint Joe Joe's [9,9,8.5]
